We want to introduce you to our brand-new YouTube channel: @ClassicalofBirdland, a place created with love for everyone who finds comfort and beauty in classical music. Our hope is to build a warm and inspiring community where we can share performances, discoveries, and meaningful musical moments together :)

Thank you for listening and for always being there! üå±üåü

‚ú¨ ABOUT US ‚ú¨

We are Mu Dimon and Rubio Faviere, the musicians behind Songs of Birdland. We record and produce all the music and videos you see in our own studio, with great dedication and a deep love for jazz and classical music. Every piece is an original creation made for all of you :)


‚ú¨ THANKS ‚ú¨
